### CM Shop Order API - Testes

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7203
@authToken = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 2. Swagger UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger

### 3. Listar todos os pedidos (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4. Buscar pedido por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/1

### 5. Buscar pedidos por usuário
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/user/test-user-123

### 6. Criar novo pedido
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderHeader": {
    "userId": "test-user-123",
    "couponCode": "DESCONTO10",
    "discountAmount": 10.00,
    "purchaseAmount": 150.00,
    "firstName": "João",
    "lastName": "Silva",
    "phone": "(11) 99999-9999",
    "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
    "cardNumber": "1234567812345678",
    "cvv": "123",
    "expiryMonthYear": "12/25",
    "cartTotalItems": 2,
    "paymentStatus": false
  },
  "orderDetails": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "count": 2,
      "productName": "Produto Teste 1",
      "price": 50.00
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "count": 1,
      "productName": "Produto Teste 2",
      "price": 60.00
    }
  ]
}

### 7. Atualizar status de pagamento (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/1/payment-status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "paymentStatus": true
}

### 8. Atualizar pedido (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "orderHeader": {
    "id": 1,
    "userId": "test-user-123",
    "couponCode": "DESCONTO15",
    "discountAmount": 15.00,
    "purchaseAmount": 145.00,
    "firstName": "João",
    "lastName": "Silva",
    "phone": "(11) 99999-9999",
    "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
    "cardNumber": "1234567812345678",
    "cvv": "123",
    "expiryMonthYear": "12/25",
    "cartTotalItems": 2,
    "paymentStatus": true
  },
  "orderDetails": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "orderHeaderId": 1,
      "productId": 1,
      "count": 2,
